data.description: If you are looking for a country home with plenty of room then this is the house for you!  Do you like to cook? The kitchen in this home has room for the whole family and areas to crafts with the kids on the huge island. Included in this kitchen is a beverage area and coffee bar. The kitchen is open to a large living room. The primary bedroom has a walk in closet and a bathroom out of a 5 star hotel! The 2nd primary bedroom includes a large walk in shower. This is truly a home to grow in and enjoy for years to come.
